        "zh": "PMBOK指南",
        "en": "PMBOK Guide"
      },
      "definition": {
        "jp": "PMBOKの内容を書籍や電子書籍にまとめたものを「PMBOKガイド」といいます。",
        "zh": "将PMBOK的内容整理成书籍或电子书的版本称为\"PMBOK指南\"。",
        "en": "The compilation of PMBOK content into books or e-books is called the \"PMBOK Guide\"."
      },
